{"tid":1627861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暫時不要再裝修，起碼等美國過埋幾條法案先，Solomon Yue 都有提水","createTime":"2019-10-05T18:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:17:10.000Z","uid":289768,"like":110,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"1cad4c4e3860ab630fe5fdac4734acd60b66ae3e","tid":1627861,"uid":289768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:25:03.000Z","msg":"暫時頂籠裝飾好喇，美國個幾條法案好重要<br />\n禁蒙面法其中一個主要目的，就係激嬲港人，激化衝突，製造暴力場面，打磕搶，火光四起，全力阻止美國法案通過，同時為緊急法其餘十幾條條例，製造藉口，什至引兵入港平亂（雖然講左好耐都未到，但中共一直有做準備隨時出兵）<br />\n現階段已經對中資紅企等產生阻嚇作用，黑幫福建幫等消聲匿跡（因現在大家會還拖），暫時很足夠了<br />\n暫時裝修意義不大，反而負面影響較多，起碼等美國d法案通過埋先（Solomon Yue twitter都有提水）<br />\n罷買，頂多裝飾已很足夠"},{"pid":"976af0e4a6c8e25f1391c6472603ae2de44da292","tid":1627861,"uid":285413,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:39:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家最近瘋狂得像野獸🙈<br />\n諗吓點解淋病會推條更惡嘅惡法先?<br />\n你覺得佢on9?年青人唔好太天真<br />\n佢後面好多人，<br />\n佢想火上加油我哋係咪要諗吓唔好中計呢?<br />\n就如1/7嗰日立法會擺空城計引君入甕咁<br />\n<br />\n點解唔和理非一陣? 等美國個法案過哂先呢?<br />\n如果我哋個形象喺外國人眼中都暴埋，<br />\n就冇人支援㗎喇<br />\n<br />\n冷靜"},{"pid":"908631999bd67d2252eaf561a800353851ca9950","tid":1627861,"uid":54228,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:56:28.000Z","msg":"堅守四大原則<br />\n<strong>黑</strong>裝修，<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span>裝飾，<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span>罷買，<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span>幫襯"},{"pid":"d29beea2fb420b9b69b73eea6afb6dcb837ea35a","tid":1627861,"uid":54824,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:57:19.000Z","msg":"各位 請讓港共人士 <br />\n享被制裁榮耀 為國捐軀<br />\n<br />\n畀美國做佢哋嘅效果 <br />\n好似好過自己做"},{"pid":"2e006a8779ef09443fd48dcc0f473ea0de2d8792","tid":1627861,"uid":306405,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:12:48.000Z","msg":"唔支持。 集中五大訴求。 裝修燒鋪極為難睇，十足真暴徒。 今日已經有好多外國朋友係咁send相俾我問點解啲示威者會變成咁樣，趁火打劫"},{"pid":"af864630bdfd5c9cb7953709910bcd83eb8b5f4d","tid":1627861,"uid":62926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:52:54.000Z","msg":"火上加油就係柒婆嘅目的<br />\n務求令我地外國戰線失利"},{"pid":"18e51914e73d6da291a0b927235aafaade71e2da","tid":1627861,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:55:21.000Z","msg":"同你推"},{"pid":"d2c4c5f03ee48b79ee464c0fc618f9e5c7ec11c7","tid":1627861,"uid":61499,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:56:22.000Z","msg":"美國佬有潔癖<br />\n已經留意緊裝修問題<br />\nSolomon 都出聲"},{"pid":"4d5225fcd318990ccc06a083aae56372f2581e15","tid":1627861,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:56:50.000Z","msg":"推下啦"},{"pid":"ff7de5264bd520eb023eab0042c02cc580215531","tid":1627861,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:58:34.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"230fe6fc16c25d5de577aa194d607c5f9bf226f0","tid":1627861,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:58:55.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79046899241bf523d47af84e781552aa33dff695","tid":1627861,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:58:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18bd2b1061108fa1435eb328fb4d7ac0dbc5a7de","tid":1627861,"uid":162380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:59:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"07f3903f86c9dc3266a539afb83fec97bc19a29b","tid":1627861,"uid":21699,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T20:00:01.000Z","msg":"所羅門幾時有提水唔好裝修？<br />\n<br />\n比source黎睇下先<br />\n<br />\n佢淨係提水話唔好搞臨時政府"},{"pid":"d933be1ab89e0221b0831ad81e549b89a90cbce7","tid":1627861,"uid":21699,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"07f3903f86c9dc3266a539afb83fec97bc19a29b","tid":1627861,"uid":21699,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":